*DESCRIPTION_START
You see one of the many homeless ghouls of Salicae, an obvious victim of
starvation and malnutrition. Its eyes hold a peculiar glimmering of pure,
animal cunning. This is the sort of ghoul which, unable to make a home here,
usually migrates to other worlds, other graveyards, in hopes of better eating.
*DESCRIPTION_END
STEALABLE

