NUMBER 3215
NAME Grave Street
REGION 4
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CHANNEL 85
MONSTER_GROUP 19
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This end of Grave Street is fairly quiet, though you can see thickening crowds
to the east. Black buildings, with a few white ones mixed in, stand away from
the street as though avoiding it, though none that you see here have yards or
anything in front of them... just open space. Salicae's bone gates form
the barrier between here and the rest of the realm of Idemmu Ag.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 3216
ITEM 0 68 ADJ1=178 VAL1=120 UNLOCKED OPEN VAL2=3214
EXTEND 0 carved from solid bone
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
From this side, the gates of the city seem perfectly ordinary, save only for
the curving spikes, slanted against the path of an outgoing traveller.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB LOOK 0
 EQUAL FLAG3 100
ENDIF
IFENTRY
 IFVAR INTNUM77 = 0
  EQUAL INTNUM77 1
  ECHO PLAYER A helpful ghoul approaches you and rasps, "You look like a newcomer. Be sure to watch out for anyone who looks really hungry."
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL -1
 IFVAR FLAG3 = 100
  ECHO PLAYER Perhaps the spikes on the gate serve to keep in the largest creatures in the city?
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
