NUMBER 3217
NAME Grave Street
REGION 4
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CHANNEL 85
MONSTER_GROUP 19
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
People - or ghouls, at least - surround you here, a crowd of them going about
their everyday business much like people anywhere are inclined to do. A few of
the undead citizens resemble living persons you know, the majority of them pay
you little attention or, at most, raise one ridged eyebrow at you before
passing on their way. After all, this is Salicae, the crossroads of Iddemu Ag.
They've seen it all before.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 3216
EXIT SE 3224
ITEM 0 465 ADJ1=348 ADJ2=25
EXTEND 0 with a white roof
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
This wide building has several small turret-style towers rising above it. A few
windows of clear oilskin look down on you, reminding you of eyes.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB SMELL -1
 ECHO PLAYER You smell mostly cooking meat, but you can make out the traces of various other scents, rotting garbage being the strongest.
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
 ECHO PLAYER You hear the sounds of the city... an argument between two inhabitants that may soon grow into a fight... a gentleman wishing someone a nice day in a happy, rasping voice.
ENDIF





