NUMBER 3220
NAME Meat Street
REGION 4
MONSTER_GROUP 19
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CHANNEL 85
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
As you make your way along the street you notice that the crowds take a
special effort to stay on its south side here, curving like a stream around a
large, heavy stone placed in its bed. A walled structure on the north side
seems to be the reason, drawing every gaze to it as surely as it repels their
walking feet. Perhaps its quieting influence is what has reduced the noise of
the crowd to a standstill, empty of anything but the pattering of bare, clawed
feet.
*DESCRIPTION_END
