*DESCRIPTION_START
A black townhouse looms over the street here like a brooding cliff of brick
and mortar or an island of rock rising from the pressing sea of the undead
crowd. Small children skirt its edges, daring each other in their high-pitched
rasping voices to touch its walls.
*DESCRIPTION_END

